track_notes: You can park on the road somewhere and start in the forest until the crest where there is enouth room for a dipole

Nice path to the top of this summit, but the sloope is a bit hard! Mostly in the forest, you will cross a small river Le Riou, if you come in summertime bring a lot of water and good shoes. GSM is OK, Local repeater R6 and DMR are OK.
